Dataset Used

Chess Pieces Dataset (85×85)
Source: Kaggle – Salman Sheikh
Link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/s4lman/chess-pieces-dataset-85x85

This dataset contains 517 images of chess pieces collected from Chess.com, resized to 85×85 pixels.
The images are organized into six classes: bishop, king, knight, pawn, queen, and rook.
Multiple board themes are included to capture variations in piece design and appearance.

The dataset is used for image classification tasks and is suitable for training computer vision models to recognize individual chess pieces.


